          <msContents>
            <summary>Ziq Chants, መጽሐፈ፡ ዚቅ፡, Mäzmur Chants</summary>
            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
              <locus from="1r" to="139v" facs="005">Fols 1r–139v</locus>
              <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1979Mashaf">Maṣḥafa ziq</title>
              <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
              <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                <locus target="#139v" facs="145">Fol. 139v</locus>
                <q><foreign xml:lang="gez">ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአፈጸመኒ፡ በፍሥሕኀ፡</foreign></q>
                <q>“Blessed be God who helped me to finish in health and peace and forgiveness… on
                  1951 E.C., Mäggabit 9 (= January 17, 1959), finished in the reign of Ḫaylä
                  Śǝllase.”</q>
                <date calendar="ethiopian" when-custom="1951" when="1959">1951 E.C., Mäggabit 9 (= January 17, 1959)</date>
              </colophon>
            </msItem>

            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
